| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0864 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 86fd4a7b-422b-5ddc-b7b4-4b3f768dc88c"
